name: INPRISON SHAPE T-Shirt, Black with Silver Barbed Wire Design, M - XL
description:
Medium T-shirts Printed on AAA Alstyle T-shirt,  6 oz. 100% Cotton Tubular Jersey.  Double-needle bottom hem and sleeves.  Shoulder-to-shoulder tape.  Preshrunk to minimize shrinkage.

Large and XL T-shirts Printed on AAA Alstyle T-shirts 5.5 oz 100% Ringspun Cotton Tubular T-Shirt.  Super-soft ringspun cotton. Tight print-face for ease of printing. ¾”  Set-in collar.  Double-needle bottom hem and sleeves. Shoulder-to-shoulder tape.  Pre-shrunk to minimize shrinkage. 

Medium Shirts have a 20" body width.

Large Shirts have a 22" body width.

X-Large Shirts have a 24" body width.

INPRISON SHAPE is a trademarked brand.  All INPRISON SHAPE Tees come with the tagless INPRISON SHAPE label screen printed on, and the AAA Alstyle tear away tags for you convenience.

Please note that INPRISON SHAPE t-shirts are each individually screen printed by hand.  Because automated printing machines are not used, INPRISON SHAPE Tees have a more personal custom look.  This means the design and label on each and every Tee will be unique with a slightly different look and finish. 

InPrison SHAPE is an expression of fitness and self confidence styled towards all types of athletes.
